                             @{b}FolioworX Player@{ub}
                      Kodak Photo CD Player Program

               Copyright © 1994-1995 by Corporate Media OHG
                         Written by Olaf Barthel

                     I.   @{" About the FolioworX Player " link Informationen}
                     II.  @{" Settings                   " link Einstellungen}
                     III. @{" Icon tooltypes             " link Piktogramm-Merkmale}
